<!--Shidori Shrine (Nirasaki)--> (Miyauchi, {{ill|Yurihama, Tottori|en}}
<!--Shidori Shrine (Nirasaki)-->, [[Tottori Prefecture]])
* ''Shidori Shrine (倭文神社)'' in ''Kume District, Hōki Province'' – {{ill|Shidori Shrine (Kurayoshi)|en}}
<!--Shidori Shrine (Nirasaki)--> (Shizu, {{ill|Kurayoshi, Tottori|en}}
